# Content/Posts System вҖ” Architecture Review

## Overview

This document defines the technical architecture for the Content/Posts System, covering post creation, media upload/processing, video handling via Mux, content feed, engagement features (likes, comments, bookmarks), and ephemeral content (stories/reels).

