## 4. Mux Video Integration

### Configuration

```typescript
// Environment variables
MUX_TOKEN_ID=             // API Token ID
MUX_TOKEN_SECRET=         // API Token Secret
MUX_WEBHOOK_SECRET=       // Webhook signature verification
```

### Upload Flow

```
1. Creator initiates video upload
   в””в”Җв”Җ POST /api/media/video/upload-url
   
2. MuxService creates direct upload
   в””в”Җв”Җ Mux API: POST /video/v1/uploads
   в””в”Җв”Җ Returns: upload URL + upload ID
   
3. Client uploads video directly to Mux
   в””в”Җв”Җ Uses returned upload URL (no server involvement)
   
4. Mux processes video automatically
   в””в”Җв”Җ Generates: thumbnails, multiple qualities, HLS streams
   
5. Mux sends webhook on completion
   в””в”Җв”Җ POST /api/webhooks/mux
   в””в”Җв”Җ Event: video.asset.ready
   
6. WebhookController updates Media record
   в””в”Җв”Җ processingStatus: completed
   в””в”Җв”Җ Stores: playbackId, thumbnailUrl, duration, etc.
```

### Webhook Handling

```typescript
// Webhook events to handle
- video.upload.created     // Upload started
- video.upload.asset_ready // Transcoding complete
- video.asset.ready        // Asset playable
- video.asset.errored      // Processing failed
```

### Playback

```typescript
// Mux playback URLs
const playbackUrl = `https://stream.mux.com/${playbackId}.m3u8`; // HLS
const thumbnailUrl = `https://image.mux.com/${playbackId}/thumbnail.jpg`;
const gifUrl = `https://image.mux.com/${playbackId}/animated.gif`;
```

