## 6. Feed Query Optimization

### Subscribed Feed Query

```sql
-- Optimized with cursor-based pagination
SELECT p.*, creator.handle, creator.display_name, creator.avatar_url
FROM posts p
INNER JOIN creator_profiles creator ON p.creator_id = creator.id
INNER JOIN subscriptions sub ON sub.creator_id = creator.id
WHERE sub.user_id = :userId
  AND sub.status = 'active'
  AND p.status = 'published'
  AND p.published_at <= now()
  AND (p.expires_at IS NULL OR p.expires_at > now())
  AND p.published_at < :cursor  -- Cursor for pagination
ORDER BY p.published_at DESC
LIMIT :limit
```

### Indexes (Already Defined)

```
