## 8. Stories/Reels Content Type Handling

### Differentiation

| Aspect | Post | Story | Reel |
|--------|------|-------|------|
| PostType | `post` | `story` | `reel` |
| Duration | Permanent | 24 hours | Permanent |
| expiresAt | null | `now + 24h` | null |
| Media | Multiple images/1 video | 1 image/short video | 1 vertical video |
| Comments | Optional | Disabled | Optional |
| Feed | Main feed | Stories bar | Reels feed |

### Story Expiration

```typescript
// Scheduled job (runs hourly)
async cleanupExpiredStories() {
  await prisma.post.updateMany({
    where: {
      postType: 'story',
      expiresAt: { lte: new Date() },
      status: 'published',
    },
    data: {
      status: 'archived',
    },
  });
}
```

