## 11. Security Considerations

| Concern | Mitigation |
|---------|------------|
| Unauthorized media access | Signed CloudFront URLs with expiration |
| Webhook spoofing | Verify Mux webhook signatures |
| Large file attacks | Enforce max file sizes (20MB image, 5GB video) |
| Content injection | Sanitize post content (XSS prevention) |
| Access control bypass | Server-side access check on every media/post request |

